fields.name: v_Stateline
fields.expression:
iif(Agent_CompanyNumber= '0000014' and Stateline='5','X'
,iif(Agent_CompanyNumber= '0000097' ,'C'
,iif(Agent_CompanyNumber= '0000090'    and LTRIM(RTRIM(PolicySymbol))='HP','4'
,iif(Agent_CompanyNumber= '0000090'    and LTRIM(RTRIM(PolicySymbol))='SBP','5'
,iif(Agent_CompanyNumber= '0000090'    and LTRIM(RTRIM(PolicySymbol))='FP','1'
,Stateline)))))

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
Stg.PolicySymbol, 
Stg.PolicyNumber, 
Stg.ModuleNumber, 
Stg.RiskState, 
Stg.Transactions, 
Stg.Agent_CompanyNumber, 
Stg.MajorPeril, 
Stg.CoverageEffectiveDate, 
Stg.PolicyEffectiveDate, 
Stg.PolicyExpirationDate, 
Stg.CededWrittenPremium, 
Stg.AccountingMonthYear, 
Stg.Stateline, 
Stg.AnnualStatementLine, 
COALESCE(LKP.POLICY_KEY,LATEST_POL.POLICY_KEY,'Not Applicable') AS POLICY_KEY
,stg.CommissionRate as CommissionRate
,stg.OriginalPremiumCancelAmount  as OriginalPremiumCancelAmount
,stg.Unit as Unit
FROM
 dbo.Ceded_PolicyReinsurance_Stg stg LEFT JOIN (Select POLICY_SYMBOL,POLICY_NUMBER,Module_Number,min(POLICY_KEY) as Policy_Key,min(company_Number) as Company_Number from dbo.lkp_policy_key 
 group by POLICY_SYMBOL,POLICY_NUMBER,Module_Number
 )lkp
on stg.PolicySymbol=lkp.POLICY_SYMBOL
AND Stg.PolicyNumber=lkp.POLICY_NUMBER
and Stg.ModuleNumber=lkp.Module_Number
and Stg.Agent_CompanyNumber NOT IN 
('0000001','0000019','0000024','0000025','0000026','0000032','0000034')
 LEFT JOIN ( SELECT A.POLICY_SYMBOL,B.POLICY_NUMBER,B.POLICY_KEY FROM 
 (select 
 POLICY_SYMBOL,POLICY_NUMBER,MAX(MODULE_NUMBER) AS LATEST_MODULE_NUMBER FROM dbo.lkp_policy_key
 GROUP BY  POLICY_SYMBOL,POLICY_NUMBER) A JOIN  dbo.lkp_policy_key B
 ON A.POLICY_SYMBOL=B.POLICY_SYMBOL AND A.POLICY_NUMBER=B.POLICY_NUMBER AND A.LATEST_MODULE_NUMBER=B.MODULE_NUMBER
 )LATEST_POL
 ON STG.POLICYSYMBOL=LATEST_POL.POLICY_SYMBOL 
 AND STG.POLICYNUMBER=LATEST_POL.POLICY_NUMBER
 AND Stg.Agent_CompanyNumber  IN ('0000019')
